{"id": "1514113731364393052", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "177811476596129792", "author_name": "haihomi", "author_bot": false, "content": "空いてる所に突っ込め、承知しました", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T03:47:24.430000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514115133679603714", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1511058757633704047", "author_name": "kiripo0080", "author_bot": false, "content": "動かし方が違うんかしらへんけど、サルバの2コスとワンダとファイント札しかぶん回さないから沙耶の狂気打てへん…2凸でけたからレベ上げおわたら沙耶あうとカーシアINでええんかな、、", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T03:52:58.768000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1514115133117300796", "filename": "Screenshot_20260610-124125.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2181282, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1514115133117300796/Screenshot_20260610-124125.png?ex=6a336b9a&is=6a321a1a&hm=c3ebfc494317c4f1fbf3b0601d1a0b5be7a727bad991952fc4dedeb1d639276f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514116122335641640", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "忘却はコンセプト編成組むならそれに振り切った方が楽しいので、極論サルバドルが１番いらないっす！\nサルバドル無いと厳しいとかであればワンダの方が先に抜けるかなって感じになるとは思います。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T03:56:54.482000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
